---
---
<div class="qs-section reveal" style="transition-delay:.2s">
  <div class="section-tag">Quem Somos</div>
  <div class="qs-card">
    <div class="qs-img-wrap">
      <img src="/images/quem-somos.webp" alt="@goleirodeeliteof" class="qs-img" />
      <div class="qs-img-fade"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="qs-body">
      <div class="qs-handle">@goleirodeeliteof</div>
      <h2 class="qs-title">Especializados em Um Único Atleta: o Goleiro.</h2>
      <p class="qs-text">
        Não treinamos todo mundo. Treinamos só goleiros — e já foram <strong>+1.200 em todo o Brasil</strong>.
        O <span class="qs-accent">Método Goleiro 2.0</span> é focado em explosão, força e velocidade para quem defende o gol. Nada genérico. Tudo específico.
      </p>
      <p class="qs-text">
        Uma sessão com personal custa <strong>R$150</strong>. Dois meses do programa custam menos do que 2 aulas. <strong>R$300 único</strong> — sem mensalidade, sem academia obrigatória.
      </p>
      <div class="qs-stats">
        <div class="qs-stat"><span class="qs-n">73K</span><span class="qs-l">Seguidores</span></div>
        <div class="qs-stat"><span class="qs-n">+1.2K</span><span class="qs-l">Goleiros treinados</span></div>
        <div class="qs-stat"><span class="qs-n">100%</span><span class="qs-l">Online</span></div>
      </div>
      <a href="https://instagram.com/goleirodeeliteof" target="_blank" class="qs-ig">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
          <path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zM12 0C8.741 0 8.333.014 7.053.072 2.695.272.273 2.69.073 7.052.014 8.333 0 8.741 0 12c0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98C8.333 23.986 8.741 24 12 24c3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98C15.668.014 15.259 0 12 0zm0 5.838a6.162 6.162 0 1 0 0 12.324 6.162 6.162 0 0 0 0-12.324zM12 16a4 4 0 1 1 0-8 4 4 0 0 1 0 8zm6.406-11.845a1.44 1.44 0 1 0 0 2.881 1.44 1.44 0 0 0 0-2.881z"/>
        </svg>
        Ver no Instagram
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .qs-section { width: 100%; max-width: 580px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

  .qs-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden; background: var(--card); position: relative;
  }
  .qs-card::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0;
    width: 80px; height: 3px; background: var(--neon);
  }
  .qs-card::after {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0;
    width: 3px; height: 80px; background: var(--neon);
  }

  .qs-img-wrap { width: 100%; height: 260px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; }
  .qs-img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: top center;
    display: block;
  }
  .qs-img-fade {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent 40%, var(--card) 100%);
  }

  .qs-body { padding: 20px 28px 32px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }

  .qs-handle { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: .72rem; color: var(--neon); letter-spacing: .06em; }

  .qs-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 1.9rem;
    line-height: 1.05; color: var(--white); letter-spacing: .04em;
  }
  .qs-text { font-size: .92rem; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.7; }
  .qs-text strong { color: var(--white); font-weight: 700; }
  .qs-accent { color: var(--neon); font-weight: 700; }

  .qs-stats {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr);
    border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 3px; overflow: hidden; margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .qs-stat {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
    padding: 14px 6px; gap: 3px; border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .qs-stat:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .qs-n { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--neon); line-height: 1; }
  .qs-l { font-size: .67rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gray); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .07em; text-align: center; }

  .qs-ig {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--muted); border-radius: 3px; padding: 9px 16px;
    font-size: .82rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gray); text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: .04em; text-transform: uppercase; transition: all .15s; align-self: flex-start;
  }
  .qs-ig:hover { border-color: var(--neon); color: var(--neon); }

  @media (max-width: 480px) { .qs-body { padding: 16px 18px 28px; } }
</style>
